Of course, padding cannot be considered a universal substitute for a longer duration data sequence. The upper-right panel of Fig. 11 shows the same input wave frequencies (5.0 mHz and 5.4 mHz), only with the resultant wave now present throughout the full ∼110\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
