Beyond the basic descriptions of whether the mode is “leaky” or “trapped”, the azimuthal integer wave number, m, defines whether the waves are the so-called “sausage”, “kink”, or “fluting” modes. The sausage mode has m=0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
