Table 1 summarizes the average properties of some of the various MHD waves in small-scale magnetic structures, reviewed in this section. As evidenced, the mean periods and phase speeds measured in different studies have wide ranges on the order 34–754 s and 13–270 km s-1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
